* Access Files\nin Volumes
** Standard path format
***_ /Volumes/<catalog>/<schema>/<volume>/<path>
***_ POSIX-style path
** Works with
***_ Apache Spark
***_ pandas
***_ SQL queries
***_ dbutils.fs commands
** No cloud credentials needed
***_ Unity Catalog handles authentication
** External volumes: also accessible via
***_ abfss:// cloud storage URI
***_ Governed by volume permissions
** File operations (dbutils.fs)
***_ ls: list files
***_ cp: copy files
@endmindmap
